window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A woman with a knack for cheating death tries to avoid the mistakes of her past lives in the first book of a gripping dark fantasy series.</b></p> <p>Death has a funny way of finding Lynette Heversham. After three villainous lifetimes—marked by pain, betrayal, and increasingly violent demises—Lynette still has no idea why she's been cursed with being reborn again and again. When she awakens as her younger self for the fourth time, she quickly realizes this life is her last chance to get it right.</p> <p>With the guidance of the gods, Lynette sets out to leave her wicked ways behind and forge a new path. Escaping her doomed engagement and the machinations of her adoptive noble family will be no easy task. As she courts scandal and shocks everyone by joining the empress's army, she's thrust into a world rife with demonic beasts and dangerous enemies.</p> <p>The key to Lynette's survival will be unlocking the long-ignored power in her core. For she'll need her newfound skills, all the knowledge gained from her past lives, and the gods' favor in order to change her fate . . .</p> <p>Combining magic, romance, action, and spectacular world-building, <i>Renewal</i> is the first installment of a unique dark fantasy series that's perfect for fans of otome and role-playing games.</p> <p><b>The first volume of the hit LitRPG adventure series—with more than 450,000 views on Royal Road—now available on Kindle, Kindle Unlimited, and Audible!</b></p>"; 
